ComicInfo.Summary:
OverviewEven as She-Cat, Tara and Ms.Victory stop Randall Crowley, his gang and their giant mechanical octopus, the Machiavellian Stella Stargaze sets her sights on the next gem to steal Tara's mega-rich father, T. C. Fremont. See the origin of Stella Stargaze, and her secret weapon. See Ms. Vistory lift a king-sized flaccid fake octopus and Tara in an evening gown, rolling on the floor in a cat-fight with Stella. Guest-starring Captain Freedom, Riot O'Rourke , T. C. Fremont and The Great Leolani. "The Hypnotic Eye", written by Bill Black, drawn by Mark Propst and inked by Mark Heike. Then, Moon's Mind Masquerade continues in "Mind Games". Colt pays a visit to writer Don Secrease in a preemptive first strike, and asks for his help in trapping Montague Moon. Don agrees, but has he been double-crossed? Written and pencilled by Secrease, inked by Mark Heike and Secrease. Color cover by Bill Black, full color throughout.
